dc_title_s: Central America, north coast of Panama, Bahía Concepción to Punta Brava (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. "From a U.S. chart to 1985 and Instituto Geografico Nacional and U.S. Naval Oceanographic surveys to 1987." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram. Map No. 26042. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
